{"tid":729641,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［只此一家］90後閒聊活動tg 谷","createTime":"2018-07-04T17:33:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T09:40:04.000Z","uid":175660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d237c34efc45507083bfdb84386bfa02baeee697","tid":729641,"uid":175660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T17:33:10.000Z","msg":"年青人，究竟有咩嘢驅使你想入谷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無論你係讀緊書，定係做緊嘢，只要你係90後，都好歡迎你加入我地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢度係一個社交平台，目的係俾大家認識下志同道合的朋友仔、擴闊生活圈子。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n發言絕對自由。但如有發現任何人故意作出不當或騷擾嘅行為，admin就會即時處理。<br />\n<br />\n男女、年齡比例盡量保持平均，亦會定時清走長期潛水的谷友～<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多，去link～ <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAENKa0Suy2Tvem44iA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAENKa0Suy2Tvem44iA&d=QI3%2Bix5GhDl9L2D%2BKypL%2FP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=c2e0fe50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAENKa0Suy2Tvem44iA</a>"},{"pid":"c42c174c04db6a8c0f8bde0fa315e097bcbccc05","tid":729641,"uid":175660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T17:34:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda25d6797e5874fd8c317d85529cd5c0e0f0ede","tid":729641,"uid":175660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T17:36:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1abdf1f269d2b325e951a4834cb56cdc9657ed51","tid":729641,"uid":107279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T18:46:28.000Z","msg":"係想屌閪呀! 屌你個閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916a947f1329b0408f5f7ad717632e38d303f386","tid":729641,"uid":175660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a